#- International News§0
§0-------------------§0
§0Dust settles as peace§0
§0is declared.§0
§0
§0 The Chimeria Alliance§0
§0quickly fell apart when§0
§0Volterra broke into§0
§0the Ruin vault almost a§0
§0week ago. The server§0
§0was tense in what§0
§0seemed to be§0
§0

#- International News§0
§0-------------------§0
§0a very long lasting§0
§0stalemate. However§0
§0when the war seemed§0
§0to be drawing closer§0
§0to "an end" both sides§0
§0discovered what they§0
§0thought to be a covert§0
§03rd party. Supposedly§0
§0members of Cantina§0
§0and Bigdogs§0
§0

#- International News§0
§0-------------------§0
§0had a plot to destroy§0
